Alignment Tools
When multiple components are selected, the Alignment Toolbar appears above the canvas with options to:

Align horizontally: Left, center, or right align selected components
Align vertically: Top, middle, or bottom align selected components
Distribute: Space components evenly horizontally or vertically
When moving or resizing components, alignment guidelines automatically appear to help snap components to the edges and centers of other components on the canvas.

